Class SpriteInspectorEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.wuic.engine.Engine
      • com.github.wuic.engine.NodeEngine
        • com.github.wuic.engine.core.SpriteInspectorEngine
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<Engine>

    @EngineService(injectDefaultToWorkflow=true,
               isCoreEngine=true)
public class SpriteInspectorEngine
extends NodeEngine

    This engine computes sprites for a set of images. It let the next engine do their job and get the result to analyze a potential aggregated image.

    Since:
    0.4.4
